data.description:
Welcome to this exceptional home that offers a blend of remarkable features for the ideal Florida lifestyle. From the moment you step onto the property, you'll be captivated by the extensive amenities it provides.The centerpiece of this property is an expansive, sparkling pool, complemented by a screened enclosure, perfect for those leisurely dips and outdoor gatherings. Your enjoyment extends to the generously sized half-acre yard, surrounded by a complete privacy fence, creating a haven for relaxation and outdoor activities. Additionally, a 10x14 shed offers valuable storage space for your convenience. For the auto or boat enthusiast, the property boasts a three-car garage with a covered area designed specifically for RV or boat parking. This versatility ensures all your vehicles and toys have a secure home. 
Stepping inside, you'll be welcomed by an inviting open floor plan that beautifully separates the living spaces. With a design that prioritizes functionality and aesthetic appeal, you'll be delighted by the details. The heart of the home is the kitchen, which features stunning 42-inch upper cabinetry, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances, including a microwave and stove. Tile flooring enhances both the visual appeal and ease of maintenance. 
The kitchen opens seamlessly to the living room and dining area, creating a spacious and inviting environment for entertaining and everyday living. The neutral paint colors throughout the home provide a soothing backdrop, making it easy for you to personalize and decorate to your taste. 
A distinct feature of this property is the secondary living space located in the rear of the home. Its versatility knows no bounds, as it can be transformed into a music room, game room, Florida room, home school, or adapted for any purpose that suits your lifestyle. 
This property truly offers the perfect blend of outdoor and indoor living, ensuring you have a comfortable and flexible space to create lifelong memories. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home.
